fields.name: Esprit Ruffle Shirt
fields.description: Made with high-quality fabrics, it offers a combination of comfort and elegance. Perfect for both casual and dressier occasions, this shirt adds a touch of sophistication to any outfit.

fields.name: Classic Trench Coat
fields.description: The Classic Trench Coat is a timeless outerwear piece that exudes sophistication and elegance. With its iconic double-breasted design, belted waist, and wide lapels, it adds a touch of refinement to any outfit. Made from high-quality materials, this coat is perfect for both formal and casual occasions, and it protects you from the elements while keeping you looking effortlessly stylish.

fields.name: Front Pocket Jumper
fields.description: The Front Pocket Jumper is a cozy and versatile sweater that combines comfort with style. Featuring a relaxed fit and a front pocket detail, it is the perfect addition to your casual wardrobe. Whether you pair it with jeans for a laid-back look or dress it up with a skirt, this jumper is a go-to option for a trendy and effortless outfit.

fields.name: Shirt in Stretch Cotton
fields.description: The Shirt in Stretch Cotton is a versatile piece that combines classic design with comfort. Made from a stretchy and breathable cotton fabric, it offers a tailored fit and moves with your body. Whether you wear it for work or play, this shirt is a wardrobe staple that can be easily dressed up or down, making it suitable for any occasion.

fields.name: Only Check Trouser
fields.description: Only Check Trouser: The Only Check Trouser is a stylish pair of pants that features a chic checkered pattern. Made with attention to detail and a focus on quality, these trousers add a fashionable twist to your outfit. With its comfortable fit and versatile design, they can be paired with a variety of tops and shoes for a trendy and put-together look.

fields.name: Herschel supply
fields.description: This shirt is made of high quality materials

fields.name: Converse All Star Hi Plimsolls
fields.description: The Converse All Star Hi Plimsolls are iconic sneakers that have stood the test of time. With their high-top design, classic canvas upper, and rubber sole, they offer both style and comfort. Whether you're going for a casual street-style look or want to add a sporty touch to your outfit, these sneakers are a must-have for any sneaker enthusiast.

fields.name: Vintage Inspired Classic
fields.description: The Vintage Inspired Classic is a fashion item that draws inspiration from retro styles and brings them into the modern era. With its timeless design and high-quality craftsmanship, it captures the essence of vintage fashion while offering contemporary comfort and durability. Perfect for those who appreciate classic aesthetics with a modern twist, this item is a statement piece that stands out from the crowd.
